<div class="container">
  <h2 class="mt-5 primary-color">Charities Registered</h2>
  <p class="body-text-grey">In order to use our site, charities must first complete a simple registration form that includes a link to their website and a brief description of the charitiesâ€™ mission and goals. We then screen each charity to ensure they uphold Handers values. The charity is then contacted and validated by our team from which point they can begin receiving donations straightaway. It is free for charities to register with Handers</p>
  <div class="d-flex">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-lg-6" style="padding: 15px 0px">
    <% @npos.each do |npo| %>
      <div class="border rounded my-4" id='<%= "npo-#{npo.id}" %>'>
          <% if  npo.photo.attachment %>
            <%= cl_image_tag npo.photo.key, height: 300, width: 400, crop: :fill, class: "card-img-top " %>
          <% end %>
          <div class="m-3 px-3">
            <h5><strong><%= npo.name%></strong></h5>
            <%= link_to 'Visit their site', npo.url, target:"_blank" %>
            <p class="card-text"><%= npo.description %></p>
          </div>
        </div>
          <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
